1. Moj *sin* ima devet godina. (My *son* is nine years old.)
2. *Sinu* sam kupila novu igračku. (I bought a new toy for my *son*.)
3. Sve što radim, radim zbog *sina*. (Everything I do, I do for my *son*.)
4. *Sinom* upravlja porodična firma. (The family company is managed by my *son*.)
5. *Sinove* drugare smo pozvali na rođendan. (We invited my *son's* friends to his birthday party.)
6. Želim da moj *sin* postane uspešan čovek. (I want my *son* to become a successful man.)
7. Moj *sin* voli da čita knjige. (My *son* likes to read books.)
8. *Sinom* sam ponosna, uspešan je student. (I am proud of my *son*, he is a successful student.)
9. *Sinovi* su mi najveća podrška. (My *sons* are my greatest support.)
10. Moj *sin* je visok i zgodan momak. (My *son* is a tall and handsome guy.)